snippet.title: Paint the Town Red - Release Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Paint the Town Red is coming to the PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch and releasing out of Early Access on Steam on July 29th.

For more information visit https://www.southeastgames.com
Or pick up the game in Early Access right now on Steam and get a head start: https://store.steampowered.com/app/337320/Paint_the_Town_Red/
